****************************************************************************************************
****                                                                                            ****
****  Phase behavior of metastable water from large-scale simulations of a quantitatively       ****
****           accurate model near ambient conditions: The liquid-liquid critical point         ****
****                                                                                            ****
****                      Luis Enrique Coronas and Giancarlo Franzese                           ****
****                                                                                            ****
****                                Universitat de Barcelona                                    ****
****                                                                                            ****
****                            https://arxiv.org/abs/2405.10181                                ****
****                                                                                            ****
****************************************************************************************************

This folder contains the code and script to calculate the probability distribution Q(x), where
    x = B_0( X - X_C),
    X = lambda^2 sin(m/lambda) + m,
    m = B(M-M_C), and
    M = rho + s*e

To compile the code: gfrotran -o histogram_reweighting_mixed_paramSI_norm_x histogram_reweighting_mixed_paramSI_norm_x.f90
To execute: bash histogram_reweighting_mixed_paramSI_norm_x.sh

The folders containing the simulation data are available at https://doi.org/10.34810/data1755
